## Provisioning Workflow

### Step 1: Validate API Access

**Command:**
```bash
curl -X GET "{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "vultr")}}https://api.vultr.com/v2/account{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "digitalocean")}}https://api.digitalocean.com/v2/account{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "linode")}}https://api.linode.com/v4/account{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "hetzner")}}https://api.hetzner.cloud/v1/account{{/if}}" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {{vpsProvider.apiKey}}" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response:**
```json
{
  "account": {
    "balance": "-500.00",
    "pending_charges": "0.00",
    "last_payment_date": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
    "last_payment_amount": "500.00"
  }
}
```

**Error Handling:**
- ❌ 401 Unauthorized → Invalid API key, check credentials
- ❌ 429 Too Many Requests → Rate limit exceeded, wait and retry
- ❌ 500 Internal Server Error → {{capitalize vpsProvider.provider}} API issue, check status page

### Step 2: Upload SSH Public Key

**Read SSH Public Key:**
```bash
SSH_PUBLIC_KEY=$(cat {{security.sshKeyPath}}.pub)
```

**Upload to {{capitalize vpsProvider.provider}}:**
```bash
curl -X POST "{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "vultr")}}https://api.vultr.com/v2/ssh-keys{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "digitalocean")}}https://api.digitalocean.com/v2/account/keys{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "linode")}}https://api.linode.com/v4/profile/sshkeys{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "hetzner")}}https://api.hetzner.cloud/v1/ssh_keys{{/if}}" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {{vpsProvider.apiKey}}" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "{{kebabCase projectName}}-deploy-key",
    "ssh_key": "'"$SSH_PUBLIC_KEY"'"
  }'
```

**Capture SSH Key ID:**
```bash
SSH_KEY_ID=$(echo $RESPONSE | jq -r '.ssh_key.id')
```

### Step 3: Create Firewall Group

**Firewall Rules:**
```bash
FIREWALL_RULES='[
{{#each security.firewallRules}}
  {
    "protocol": "{{protocol}}",
    "port": "{{port}}",
    "source": "{{source}}"
  }{{#unless @last}},{{/unless}}
{{/each}}
]'
```

**Create Firewall:**
```bash
curl -X POST "{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "vultr")}}https://api.vultr.com/v2/firewalls{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "digitalocean")}}https://api.digitalocean.com/v2/firewalls{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "linode")}}https://api.linode.com/v4/networking/firewalls{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "hetzner")}}https://api.hetzner.cloud/v1/firewalls{{/if}}" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {{vpsProvider.apiKey}}" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "description": "{{projectName}} Firewall",
    "inbound_rules": '"$FIREWALL_RULES"'
  }'
```

**Capture Firewall ID:**
```bash
FIREWALL_ID=$(echo $RESPONSE | jq -r '.firewall.id')
```

### Step 4: Provision VPS Instance

**Create Instance Request:**
```bash
curl -X POST "{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "vultr")}}https://api.vultr.com/v2/instances{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "digitalocean")}}https://api.digitalocean.com/v2/droplets{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "linode")}}https://api.linode.com/v4/linode/instances{{/if}}{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "hetzner")}}https://api.hetzner.cloud/v1/servers{{/if}}" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {{vpsProvider.apiKey}}" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "region": "{{vpsProvider.region}}",
    "plan": "{{vpsProvider.plan}}",
    "label": "{{kebabCase projectName}}-production",
    "hostname": "{{domain.appwriteSubdomain}}.{{domain.rootDomain}}",
    "ssh_keys": ["'"$SSH_KEY_ID"'"],
    "firewall_group_id": "'"$FIREWALL_ID"'"{{#if vpsProvider.enableIPv6}},
    "enable_ipv6": true{{/if}}{{#if vpsProvider.enableBackups}},
    "backups": "enabled"{{/if}}
  }'
```

**Monitor Provisioning Status:**
```bash
INSTANCE_ID=$(echo $RESPONSE | jq -r '.instance.id')

while true; do
  STATUS=$(curl -s -X GET "{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "vultr")}}https://api.vultr.com/v2/instances/$INSTANCE_ID{{/if}}" \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer {{vpsProvider.apiKey}}" | jq -r '.instance.status')

  if [ "$STATUS" == "active" ]; then
    echo "✅ VPS provisioning complete!"
    break
  fi

  echo "⏳ VPS status: $STATUS (waiting...)"
  sleep 10
done
```

**Capture VPS IP Address:**
```bash
VPS_IP=$(curl -s -X GET "{{#if (eq vpsProvider.provider "vultr")}}https://api.vultr.com/v2/instances/$INSTANCE_ID{{/if}}" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer {{vpsProvider.apiKey}}" | jq -r '.instance.main_ip')

echo "📍 VPS IP Address: $VPS_IP"
```

### Step 5: Verify SSH Connectivity

**Test SSH Connection:**
```bash
ssh -i {{security.sshKeyPath}} -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@$VPS_IP "echo '✅ SSH connection successful!'"
```

**Update Deployment State:**
```bash
cat > deployment-state.json <<EOF
{
  "vpsProvisioned": true,
  "vpsProvider": "{{vpsProvider.provider}}",
  "instanceId": "$INSTANCE_ID",
  "vpsIp": "$VPS_IP",
  "sshKeyId": "$SSH_KEY_ID",
  "firewallId": "$FIREWALL_ID",
  "region": "{{vpsProvider.region}}",
  "plan": "{{vpsProvider.plan}}",
  "provisionedAt": "$(date -u +"%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ")"
}
EOF
```

